snippet.title: Battle Mountain Early Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Battle Mountain! The absolute best combat climbing athletes gather every 8 years to prove who is the worlds greatest. Join the roster of fighting fit characters to help achieve their dreams of holding the Crowntain at the peak of the most competitive sporting event.

Wishlist and play the demo on Steam TODAY!
